item.title: Introduction to Water Quality Testing
item.description: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h3DvCCifdr0 Uploaded on Jun 13, 2010 Introduction to Water Quality Testing - Southern Regional Aquaculture Center - Product 331 - Aims to provide some of the knowledge of water quality which is essential to pond owners and aquaculturists. The work reported in this publication was supported in part by the Southern Regional Aquaculture Center through Grant No. 2006 38500 16977 from the U.S. Department of Agriculture, Cooperative State Research, Education, and Extension Service (CSREES)
